# 4. Project Planning Phase 

# Project Planning Phase

## Introduction

Project planning is an essential phase that defines the roadmap for successful project completion. It includes task allocation, timeline estimation, milestone planning, and resource management. Proper planning ensures that every team member understands their responsibilities and that the project progresses in a systematic manner.

---

## Project Objectives

* Develop a Machine Learning model to predict Human Development Index (HDI).
* Build a Flask-based web application for user interaction.
* Perform data preprocessing and visualization.
* Evaluate the model using regression metrics.
* Deploy a user-friendly prediction system.

---

