## Sprint Planning

### Sprint 1

* Install required libraries
* Create project structure
* Download dataset

### Sprint 2

* Data preprocessing
* Data visualization
* Feature selection

### Sprint 3

* Train Linear Regression model
* Evaluate performance
* Save model

### Sprint 4

* Develop Flask application
* Design HTML pages
* Perform testing
* Upload to GitHub

---

## Project Timeline

Week 1

* Requirement Analysis
* Brainstorming

Week 2

* Dataset Collection
* Data Exploration

Week 3

* Model Development

Week 4

* Flask Deployment
* Documentation
* Testing

